# Once done this will define
#
#  PQ_FOUND - system has pq
#  PQ_INCLUDE_DIRS - the pq include directory
#  PQ_LIBRARIES - Link these to use pq
#  PQ_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using pq
